      <guid>/posts/2022-06-18-pulumi_libvirt-series/</guid>
      <description>description The idea of this series is to share my progress integrating pulumi to my workflow. While googling for pulumi + libvirt I came across Dustin&amp;rsquo;s post https://dustinspecker.com/posts/ubuntu-vm-pulumi-libvirt which is written in golang.
I have taken his work as a base, transpiled his code to python and then started to do my own thing.
