      <content>&lt;h2 id=&#34;description&#34;&gt;description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The idea of this series is to share my progress integrating pulumi to my workflow. While googling for &lt;code&gt;pulumi + libvirt&lt;/code&gt; I came across Dustin&amp;rsquo;s post &lt;a href=&#34;https://dustinspecker.com/posts/ubuntu-vm-pulumi-libvirt&#34;&gt;https://dustinspecker.com/posts/ubuntu-vm-pulumi-libvirt&lt;/a&gt; which is written in golang.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I have taken his work as a base, transpiled his code to python and then started to do my own thing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;progress&#34;&gt;progress&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;exercise nr&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;description&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_1/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;create &lt;code&gt;domain&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_2/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;create &lt;code&gt;pool&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;media_volume&lt;/code&gt; volume for .img, &lt;code&gt;vm-boot&lt;/code&gt; volume for the os&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_3/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;add serial console&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_4/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;add &lt;code&gt;cloud_init&lt;/code&gt; (user:pw)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_5/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;add &lt;code&gt;cloud_init&lt;/code&gt; (network nat)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_6/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;get &amp;ldquo;IP Address&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;VM Name&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/exercise_7/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;add network autostart&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;exercises/__main__.py&#34;&gt;exercise_final&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;change network nat -&amp;gt; br0&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
</content>
